#. See: https://docs.gtk.org/atk/enum.TextAttribute.html
#: src/orca/text_attribute_names.py:78
msgctxt "textattr"
msgid "mistake"
msgstr "памылка"

#. Translators: this attribute specifies whether the text is invisible.
